#: front-page.php:560
msgid "What position does Nico Paz play?"
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:561
msgid "Nico Paz is an attacking midfielder (CAM) known for his vision, passing range, and technical ability. He can also operate as a central midfielder (CM) or on the wings when needed."
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:564
msgid "Which clubs has Nico Paz played for?"
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:565
msgid "Nico began his youth career at Real Madrid\'s famed La Fábrica academy. He made his first-team debut for Real Madrid before joining Como 1907 in Serie A. He has also represented Argentina at various youth international levels."
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:568
msgid "How can I buy official Nico Paz merchandise?"
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:569
msgid "Official merchandise is available in the Shop section of this website. We offer authentic jerseys, apparel, accessories, and limited-edition items. All products are shipped worldwide."
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:572
msgid "What is the shipping policy?"
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:573
msgid "We ship internationally. Delivery times vary by location — typically 5–10 business days domestically and 10–20 business days internationally. You will receive a tracking number once your order is dispatched."
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:576
msgid "How can I contact Nico Paz or his management?"
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:577
msgid "For press inquiries, sponsorship opportunities, and professional requests, please use the Contact section on this website or email hello@nicopaz.com. We aim to respond within 48 hours."
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:580
msgid "Does Nico Paz have social media accounts?"
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:581
msgid "Yes! Follow Nico on Instagram, Twitter, and TikTok for exclusive behind-the-scenes content, training updates, and personal messages. Links to all official accounts can be found in the footer of this site."
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:584
msgid "What sizes are available for jerseys?"
msgstr ""

#: front-page.php:585
msgid "Our jerseys are available in sizes XS through 3XL. Please refer to the size guide on each product page for detailed measurements. If you are between sizes, we recommend sizing up for a more comfortable fit."
msgstr ""

